gameOver.haxe_doc: * Forces a game over. * @param character Character which died. Default to `boyfriend`. * @param deathCharID Character ID (name) for game over. Default to whatever is specified in the character's XML. * @param gameOverSong Song for the game over screen. Default to `this.gameOverSong` (`gameOver`) * @param lossSFX SFX at the beginning of the game over (Mic drop). Default to `this.lossSFX` (`gameOverSFX`) * @param retrySFX SFX played whenever the player retries. Defaults to `retrySFX` (`gameOverEnd`)
